results.name: Permutation of natural numbers induced when A091204 is restricted to nonprime numbers: a(n) = 1+A091245(A091204(A018252(n))).
link: Antti Karttunen, Table of n, a(n) for n = 1..10001
Index entries for sequences that are permutations of the natural numbers
formula: As a composition of related permutations:
program: isA014580(n)=polisirreducible(Pol(binary(n))*Mod(1, 2)); \\ This function from _Charles R Greathouse IV_
A002808(n)={my(k); for(k=0, primepi(n), isprime(n++)&&k--); n}; \\ This function from _M. F. Hasler_

A091204(n) = if(n<=1, n, if(isprime(n), A014580(A091204(primepi(n))), {my(pfs, t, bits, i); pfs=factor(n); pfs[, 1]=apply(t->Pol(binary(A091204(t))), pfs[, 1]); sum(i=1, #bits=Vec(factorback(pfs))%2, bits[i]<<(#bits-i))}));
results.author: _Antti Karttunen_, Aug 16 2014
